When viewing an issue's comments, work log, etc., you can either view each category by itself, or the All tab. But the All tab includes all of the Change Log items which makes for a long and messy list of things. Most times, when I'm looking for information on an issue, I want to see just the Comments and the Work Logged to get the best feel of what happened with an issue. But I can't view them at the same time, so I have to view two separate "conversations" on an issue, which is disjointed at best.

It would be great if this interface was changed so that I could selectively add/remove tabs to my current view (i.e., let me click on Comments and then click on Work Log and it would leave the comments listed and add the Work Log to the list). I think this is a good improvement, especially as more plugins are added that would add additional tabs to this section of the issue viewer.

