Jelly added comment is not searchable in Issue Navigator. Steps of reproducing:

* Use the [{{<AddComment/>}}|http://www.atlassian.com/software/jira/docs/latest/jelly.html#AddComment] tag to create a comment with "unique" keywords
* Search issue navigator with terms appear in the comment
* Nothing will return

This is due to the {{dispatchEvent}} flag being set as false, e.g. 

{code:java}
commentManager.create(issue, author, updateAuthor, commentBody, grouplevel, roleLevelId == null ? null : roleLevelId, created, updated, false);
{code}

Both 3.7 and 3.8 use different piece of code (commentService and commentManager) for this and produce the same behaviour.

